Package: scAIkit
Type: Package
Title: AI-assisted Toolkit for Single-cell RNA-seq Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Simarjot Pabla and contributors
Maintainer: Simarjot Pabla <your_email@example.com>
Description: scAIkit provides AI-assisted utilities to streamline single-cell RNA-seq analysis in R,
    including QC, normalization, batch integration, clustering, annotation, signature scoring, 
    cell-cell interaction analysis, and automated report generation.
